<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 15:12:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>富国银行警告降价对需求的影响减弱，特斯拉股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-slips-wells-fargo-warns-waning-effect-price-cuts-over-demand-2024-03-13/</link><description>周三，富国银行对全球最有价值的汽车制造商降价对其电动汽车需求影响减弱表示担忧，并将其评级下调至“减持”，特斯拉股价周三下跌约 2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-slips-wells-fargo-warns-waning-effect-price-cuts-over-demand-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳首席财务官表示海外销售将进一步疲软，中东和中国受到打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/mcdonalds-cfo-says-overseas-sales-weaken-more-middle-east-china-hit-2024-03-13/</link><description>麦当劳首席财务官伊恩·博登(Ian Borden)周三表示，受中东冲突和中国需求疲软的压力，麦当劳本季度的国际销售额将连续下降，导致其股价早盘下跌2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/mcdonalds-cfo-says-overseas-sales-weaken-more-middle-east-china-hit-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国委员会敦促对涉嫌在中国捕鱼的朝鲜劳工采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-commission-urges-action-alleged-north-korean-labor-china-fishing-2024-03-13/</link><description>美国国会一个委员会呼吁拜登政府对中国渔业中涉及朝鲜工人的强迫劳动行为采取行动，称向美国消费者销售海鲜可能有助于为朝鲜的武器计划提供资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:03:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-commission-urges-action-alleged-north-korean-labor-china-fishing-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>洛佩斯凌空抽射助10人马里诺队晋级亚冠半决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/lopes-volley-takes-10-man-marinos-into-asian-champions-league-semis-2024-03-13/</link><description>周三，十人应战的横滨水手队凭借安德森·洛佩斯的凌空抽射帮助科威尔的球队以1-0战胜山东泰山队，以总比分3-1获胜，晋级亚洲冠军联赛半决赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/lopes-volley-takes-10-man-marinos-into-asian-champions-league-semis-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国国防部称与北约举行军事人员对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-defence-ministry-says-it-held-military-staff-dialogue-with-nato-2024-03-13/</link><description>中国国防部的一份声明称，中国和北约周三在北京举行第八次军事安全政策对话。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:06:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-defence-ministry-says-it-held-military-staff-dialogue-with-nato-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者提出立法，寻求对中国房地产购买进行更多审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-lawmakers-propose-legislation-seeking-more-scrutiny-chinese-real-estate-2024-03-13/</link><description>两名美国议员将于周四提出立法，大幅扩大政府对来自中国和其他构成国家安全担忧的外国买家购买房地产的外国投资审查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-lawmakers-propose-legislation-seeking-more-scrutiny-chinese-real-estate-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：意大利与中国奇瑞就汽车工厂进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-chery-car-plant-2024-03-13/</link><description>两名消息人士告诉路透社，意大利政府正在与中国奇瑞汽车进行谈判，以吸引除 Stellantis 之外的另一家主要汽车制造商进入该国并增加国内汽车产量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-chery-car-plant-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>立法者投票后，欧洲距具有里程碑意义的人工智能规则仅一步之遥</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-lawmakers-endorse-political-deal-artificial-intelligence-rules-2024-03-13/</link><description>周三，欧洲距离采用世界上第一个人工智能规则又近了一步，欧盟立法者批准了一项临时协议，该技术的使用在各行各业和日常生活中迅速增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:22:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-lawmakers-endorse-political-deal-artificial-intelligence-rules-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔总理赢得议会信任投票，为14个月内第三次</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-confidence-third-14-months-2024-03-13/</link><description>尼泊尔总理普什帕·卡迈勒·达哈尔周三赢得议会信任投票，一周前，他在一年多的时间里组建了第三个联盟，领导一个由自由共产主义者主导的政府。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-confidence-third-14-months-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车表示其ID.UNYX车型已获得中国政府批准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-it-has-received-chinese-government-approval-idunyx-model-2024-03-13/</link><description>大众汽车集团（中国）周三表示，其唯一控股的合资企业安徽大众汽车的首款车型已获得中国政府批准。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-it-has-received-chinese-government-approval-idunyx-model-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：人工智能避开消费物价指数，中国再次陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-03-13/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过法案迫使字节跳动剥离TikTok，否则将面临禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-house-vote-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-ban-2024-03-13/</link><description>美国众议院周三以压倒性多数通过了一项法案，该法案将给 TikTok 的中国所有者字节跳动大约六个月的时间剥离这款约 1.7 亿美国人使用的短视频应用程序的美国资产，否则将面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-house-vote-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-ban-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国煤炭集团表示，美国对俄罗斯的限制是为了保持高价格，损害了出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-coal-group-says-us-curbs-russia-keep-prices-high-hurt-exports-2024-03-13/</link><description>中国一个行业组织周三警告称，美国对俄罗斯煤炭公司更严厉的制裁将在短期内使全球高热值煤炭价格保持在高位，影响俄罗斯五分之一的煤炭出口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 08:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-coal-group-says-us-curbs-russia-keep-prices-high-hurt-exports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>抵押贷款违约率上升给中国家庭带来更多痛苦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rising-mortgage-defaults-bring-more-pain-chinese-households-2024-03-13/</link><description>在中国南方城市，前金融工作者雷晓宇因抵押贷款拖欠而被收债人追捕，她不再接听电话，试图推迟不可避免的事情。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:06:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rising-mortgage-defaults-bring-more-pain-chinese-households-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着对华贸易的蓬勃发展，一些俄罗斯企业蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-with-china-booms-some-russian-companies-are-flourishing-2024-03-13/</link><description>尼基塔·米年科夫 (Nikita Minenkov) 的物流公司位于俄罗斯和中国边界的阿穆尔河附近，业务进展顺利。自从莫斯科入侵乌克兰以来，情况变得更好——公司营业额连续两年翻了一番。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-with-china-booms-some-russian-companies-are-flourishing-2024-03-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>